Hong Kong Stocks Open Lower
HONG KONG , December 28 ( Xinhua ) -- Hong Kong stocks fell 28.58 points , or 0.28 percent , to open at 10,263.62 on Monday .
The key Hang Seng Index rose 133.45 points , or 1.31 percent , to close at 10,292.20 on Thursday .
The market has remained closed since Friday to observe the Christmas holidays .
